text: Zamacois is a Hispanophone surname. == People with this surname == *Niceto de Zamacois (1820–1885), Spanish writer and historian. *Eduardo Zamacois y Zabala (1841–1871), Spanish painter. *Miguel Zamacoïs (1866–1955), French writer. *Eduardo Zamacois (1873–1971), Spanish writer. *Joaquim Zamacois (1894–1976), Spanish composer.
